Text: MUST READPAYROLL PROCEDURES FOR NEXT WEEKpst Icon will be closed on Monday in observance of the Memorial Day holiday Next week is also payroll week To make this a smooth and easy process for everyone we ask that hours andor timesheets be turned in by NOON on Friday If you anticipate that you will have hours over the weekend please make sure that we get your complete hours worked no later than am on Tuesday to avoid those additional hours not being processed on the payroll Thank you in advance for your understanding and cooperation Icon Information Consultants W Loop South Houston Tx fax mailto
